{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"title":"TokensProvider Implementations","roleHeading":"API Collection","role":"collectionGroup"},"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Instance-Methods","title":"Instance Methods","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider\/checkInstances(count:for:)"]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebadgecomponenttokensprovider\/tokensprovider-implementations"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider\/TokensProvider-Implementations"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"kind":"article","references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider":{"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebadgecomponenttokensprovider","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of badge","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"badge"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSBadge","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens provide